Recommends: libmagickcore-6.q16-6-extra, qt6-translations-l10n
Description: IPTV player with EPG support
 yuki-iptv is an IPTV player with many features, such as:
  * M3u / M3u8 / XSPF playlists support
  * XTream API support
  * TV program (EPG) support in XMLTV and JTV formats
  * Save channels as favorites
  * Stream recording
  * Channel groups
  * Playlist editor
  * TV archive / catchup
  * ...
